'''Jean-Michel Thierry de Crussol''' (1916–2011) was a [[France|French]] [[physician]] and [[art historian]]. His specialities are in [[Byzantine art|Byzantine]] and [[Armenian art]].<ref>http://www.acam-france.org/bibliographie/auteur.php?cle=thierry-jeanmichel</ref>
He was born on August 13, 1916 in [[Bagnères de Luchon]], [[France]]. He studied and got his education in Paris. He co-wrote the book ''Armenian Art'' in 1989 and also wrote many articles concerning Armenian art, especially [[Armenian architecture]].
== Works == * {{Armenian Art 1989}} * {{cite book |last=Thierry de Crussol |first=Jean-Michel |title=L'Arménie au Moyen-Âge |trans-title=Armenia in the Middle Ages |url= |edition= |series=Les Formes de la nuit |volume= |date= |origyear= |year=2000 |month= |publisher=[[:fr:Éditions Zodiaque|Éditions Zodiaque]] |location= |language=French |isbn=2-7369-0268-8 |laysummary=http://www.bibliomonde.com/livre/armenie-moyen-age--4848.html |laydate= }} * {{cite book |last=Thierry de Crussol |first=Jean-Michel |title=Monuments arméniens de Haute-Arménie |trans-title=Armenian Monuments in Upper Armenia |url= |edition= |series=Les Formes de la nuit |volume= |date= |origyear= |year=2005 |month= |publisher=[[CNRS|CNRS Éditions]] |location=[[Paris]] |language=French |isbn=2-271-06187-3 |laysummary=http://www.bibliomonde.com/livre/monuments-armeniens-haute-armenie-3563.html |laydate= }}
